Merkel-Sarkozy Meeting Today to Include ECB, EU, IMF Officials

-- B y   S t e p h a n i e   B o d o n i
-- 
2011-10-22T10:59:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/merkel-sarkozy-meeting-today-to-include-ecb-eu-imf-officials.html
A meeting tonight between German
Chancellor  Angela Merkel  and French President Nicolas Sarkozy
also will include officials from the European Union, the
 European Central Bank  and the  International Monetary Fund , said
Guy Schuller, the spokesman for Luxembourg Prime Minister Jean-
Claude Juncker.    To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephanie Bodoni in Brussels at 
